## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not capture the full spectrum of reasons behind vaccine hesitancy. The complexity of individual beliefs and the influence of cultural and regional factors are not fully explored in this report. Additionally, the data is limited to sources available up to October 2023, and new developments in vaccine research and public health policies may influence future trends in vaccine acceptance.

